    "An increase of 96.13% was the consequence of this significant enhancement in accuracy.",
    "The development of ensemble models, such as EnsemDeepCADx, represented a significant advancement in the field.",
    "By consolidating features from multiple CNNs with BLSTM and SVM, accuracy increased to 97.89%.",
    "The introduction of Vision Transformers and additional enhancements to GIEnsemformerCADx sustained this trend, despite a degree of reduced accuracy resulting from performance and complexity compromises.",
    "PolynetDWTCADx, the most recent proposed system, maintains computing efficiency while achieving a firm accuracy of 92.3%."
